snippet.title: Ukrainian fArmy release video
snippet.description:
HELP THE PEOPLE OF UKRAINE OVERCOME THE ENEMY
COME AND PLAY: https://ukrainian.itch.io/ukrainian-farmy

Official account in support of the Armed Forces of Ukraine: (https://bank.gov.ua/en/news/all/natsionalniy-bank-vidkriv-rahunok-dlya-gumanitarnoyi-dopomogi-ukrayintsyam-postrajdalim-vid-rosiyskoyi-agresiyi )

Please spread the word about this initiative. In the face of war, we are standing strong. Stand beside us. Every bit helps.
Glory to Ukraine!
